{"tid":1681173,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"商人涉 3,000 元毒品賄賂警員　警員疑曾於被告住所吸毒　控方未決定會否拘控","createTime":"2019-10-29T08:57:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T12:17:36.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"70cda890ef2bad3c2ea7cb498aae5049bbdaf117","tid":1681173,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T08:57:15.000Z","msg":"男商人被指串謀販運毒品及以總值 3,000 元的毒品賄賂一名警員，遭廉署控以一項串謀販毒及 3 項向公職人員提供利益罪，案件今於西九龍裁判法院提堂，被告暫毋須答辯，押後 12 月 13 日再訊並獲准保釋。據了解，涉案警員王得嘉疑曾於被告的住所內服食可卡因。<br />\n<br />\n控方則於庭外表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">暫時未有指示是否會拘捕及控告涉案警員</span>。據了解，被告於在 2017 年 8 月中至 9 月中期間，先後 3 次接受警員王得嘉及其他警務人員會見以提供情報，其後被告兩次以折扣價向警員王得嘉提供可卡因，其中一次王得嘉更於被告住所內服食可卡因，被告另曾免費向王得嘉提供 1 克可卡因。<br />\n<br />\n被告王偉明（59歲），被控 3 項向公職人員提供利益罪及一項串謀販運危險藥物罪。控罪指他於 2017 年 8 月 1 日至 12 月 31 日期間，無合法權限或合理辯解，兩次以折扣價向警員王得嘉提供可卡因，及在另一場合向對方免費提供約 1 克可卡因，涉案可卡因總值 3,000 元，作為使王得嘉傾向或保持傾向優待被告的誘因或報酬。被告另被控一項串謀販運危險藥物罪名，指他於同一時期，與其他不知名者串謀非法販運可卡因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%95%86%E4%BA%BA%E6%B6%89-3-000-%E5%85%83%E6%AF%92%E5%93%81%E8%B3%84%E8%B3%82%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1-%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E7%96%91%E6%9B%BE%E6%96%BC%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E4%BD%8F%E6%89%80%E5%90%B8%E6%AF%92-%E6%8E%A7%E6%96%B9%E6%9C%AA%E6%B1%BA%E5%AE%9A%E6%9C%83%E5%90%A6%E6%8B%98%E6%8E%A7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2595%2586%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B6%2589-3-000-%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%25AF%2592%25E5%2593%2581%25E8%25B3%2584%25E8%25B3%2582%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%259B%25BE%25E6%2596%25BC%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E4%25BD%258F%25E6%2589%2580%25E5%2590%25B8%25E6%25AF%2592-%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%259C%25AA%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E5%25AE%259A%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2590%25A6%25E6%258B%2598%25E6%258E%25A7%2F&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg4%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=d5a38cbe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2595%2586%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B6%2589-3-000-%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%25AF%2592%25E5%2593%2581%25E8%25B3%2584%25E8%25B3%2582%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%259B%25BE%25E6%2596%25BC%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E4%25BD%258F%25E6%2589%2580%25E5%2590%25B8%25E6%25AF%2592-%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%259C%25AA%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E5%25AE%259A%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2590%25A6%25E6%258B%2598%25E6%258E%25A7%2F&h=7e1b2237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%95%86%E4%BA%BA%E6%B6%89-3-000-%E5%85%83%E6%AF%92%E5%93%81%E8%B3%84%E8%B3%82%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1-%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E7%96%91%E6%9B%BE%E6%96%BC%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E4%BD%8F%E6%89%80%E5%90%B8%E6%AF%92-%E6%8E%A7%E6%96%B9%E6%9C%AA%E6%B1%BA%E5%AE%9A%E6%9C%83%E5%90%A6%E6%8B%98%E6%8E%A7/</a>"},{"pid":"ef285f57031c9348deb8d33d6b5f1152d62b9955","tid":1681173,"uid":136893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T09:03:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">記唔記得7、8月既時候，臨有行動前一日既連登，係充滿住遊行路線、離開方法、行動目的地既街坊整既攻略、仲有各種各樣既行動資訊整合，所有行動都係至小早半個月搞，有D 活動更加係會根據其重要性去調配，例如我記得葵青區遊行係推遲左成個月的。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n反思行動及行動數量<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">（極緊急！！！）等我教大家點再引發群眾熱情<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1680895\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1680895</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"7f30db12677efdb7ffad531eef1be466828776ff","tid":1681173,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T10:41:55.000Z","msg":"ICAC教現場享用無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7abc4dc0e8ddcfddd342bcb2789e2f714705408","tid":1681173,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T10:46:06.000Z","msg":"吸毒仲大罪過貪污wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啊唔記得咗香港警察可以唔洗遵守法律添<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00f0423392e2aa6330a23118e5275e871f0c6309","tid":1681173,"uid":128014,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T10:46:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">阿sir隊草唔駛你教<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"0f161971f2a5447bebe164264ad80efbb9b69bb6","tid":1681173,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T11:17:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72ff92db414dd31017bf5aa82d70c369a4c4d94a","tid":1681173,"uid":117729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T12:16:05.000Z","msg":"你死啦，公開警員個名，好快有人上門"},{"pid":"3060808d8190ab093bfbb519777738a710bb013e","tid":1681173,"uid":72751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00f0423392e2aa6330a23118e5275e871f0c6309","tid":1681173,"uid":128014,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T10:46:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">阿sir隊草唔駛你教<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T12:17:31.000Z","msg":"可卡因Wo"},{"pid":"5b0f0d178d51142128d20f08ed8220360cdb3b4e","tid":1681173,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T12:17:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}